Name: GetNamedSession
Text: Its purpose is to retrieve a pointer to a session object (FNamedOnlineSession) by its name.

Name: DestroySession
Text: This method is used to destroy an existing online session identified by its name

Name: AddOnCreateSessionCompleteDelegate_Handle
Text: This is a method that registers a delegate (a callback function) to be executed when the session creation process is complete.

Name: CreateSession
Text: This method is used to create a new online session

Name: FindSessions
Text: Searches for sessions matching the settings specified

Name: GetResolvedConnectString
Text: Returns the platform specific connection information for joining the match
